text:
Just started my internship at Microsoft! 💻
Day 1 and I'm already learning so much.
Excited to contribute to real-world projects! 🚀

Debugging at 3 AM hits different 🌙
When you finally find that missing semicolon...
The satisfaction is unmatched! 😅

Completed my first machine learning project today! 🤖
Built a sentiment analysis model with 85% accuracy.
Small wins matter! 💪

College vs Real World:
College: Perfect code, no bugs
Real World: 'It works, don't touch it' 😂
#RealTalk #DeveloperLife

Failed the Google interview today 😔
But learned more in 45 minutes than weeks of preparation.
Rejection is redirection! 🔄

Tips for CS students:
1. Build projects, not just assignments
2. Contribute to open source
3. Network actively
4. Never stop learning
5. Embrace failures

From zero to deployed! 🚀
Built my first full-stack web app using React and Node.js.
Feeling like I can conquer the world! 🌍

Mental health reminder for job seekers:
Your worth ≠ Job rejections
Take breaks, stay positive, keep pushing! ❤️
#MentalHealthMatters

Hackathon weekend! 24 hours of coding ahead ⏰
Team assembled, coffee stocked, let's build something amazing! ☕️💻

Just got my first job offer! 🎉
After 200+ applications and 15 interviews.
Persistence pays off! Never give up! 💪
